# Large files
*.h5
*.hdf5
*.pkl
*.pickle
*.joblib
*.zip
*.tar.gz

# Security
secrets.yaml
*.pem
*.key
*.crt

# ============================================================================
# EXCEPTIONS (files we DO want to track)
# ============================================================================

# !manifests/examples/     # Example manifests should be tracked
# !examples/**/*.md        # Example documentation should be tracked
# !docs/**/*               # All documentation should be tracked

# ============================================================================
# PHILOSOPHICAL NOTE:
# Version control is for preserving knowledge, not data.
# Code and documentation represent knowledge.
# Generated findings represent observations.
# We preserve the means of reproduction (code), not the observations themselves.
# Observations should be archived separately with proper metadata.
# ============================================================================

